{
	"nodes": [
		{
			"id": "title",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -720,
			"y": -760,
			"width": 960,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "# 无界知识：知识网络操作架构\n\n先把脑内系统外化成可拖动结构。这里不是最终方案，而是你和 Codex 共同迭代的架构白板。"
		},
		{
			"id": "group-sources",
			"type": "group",
			"x": -1760,
			"y": -470,
			"width": 520,
			"height": 850,
			"color": "4",
			"label": "1. Knowledge Sources"
		},
		{
			"id": "source-papers",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1700,
			"y": -370,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## 论文\narXiv / 期刊 / 会议 / 标准文档\n\n重点：方法、证据、局限、可复用概念"
		},
		{
			"id": "source-github",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1700,
			"y": -190,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## GitHub 技术主题\nrepo / topic / release / issue / PR\n\n重点：成熟度、生态位置、风险信号"
		},
		{
			"id": "source-web",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1700,
			"y": -10,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## 专业网页\n官方文档 / 技术博客 / 行业报告 / 法规\n\n重点：可信度、更新时间、适用边界"
		},
		{
			"id": "source-personal",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1700,
			"y": 170,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "## 个人草稿与经验\n项目经验 / 灵感 / 复盘 / 对话记录\n\n重点：场景、观察、边界、待验证问题"
		},
		{
			"id": "group-ingestion",
			"type": "group",
			"x": -1110,
			"y": -470,
			"width": 620,
			"height": 850,
			"color": "5",
			"label": "2. 捕获登记与领域路由"
		},
		{
			"id": "capture-inbox",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1040,
			"y": -390,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 110,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 捕获到 Inbox\n00-inbox/\n\n先收集原始材料，不急着完美整理"
		},
		{
			"id": "source-registry",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1040,
			"y": -230,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 来源登记\n10-sources/\n\n记录 id、URL、时间、可信度、来源类型、初步领域候选"
		},
		{
			"id": "domain-taxonomy",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1040,
			"y": -50,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 150,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## 领域门类规划\n先定义顶层知识领域\n\nAI / 软件工程 / 数据知识工程 / 安全合规 / 商业投资 / 产业行业 / 认知方法"
		},
		{
			"id": "domain-routing",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1040,
			"y": 150,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 130,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 领域路由\n给每个来源分配：\nprimary_domain + secondary_domains + tags\n\n先定归属，再做提炼"
		},
		{
			"id": "extraction",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1040,
			"y": 320,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 130,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "## 领域感知提炼\n在所属领域内提取：\nconcept / claim / method / pattern / risk\n\n避免同一知识点在多个门类重复生长"
		},
		{
			"id": "group-knowledge",
			"type": "group",
			"x": -350,
			"y": -470,
			"width": 640,
			"height": 850,
			"color": "3",
			"label": "3. Atomic Knowledge & Synthesis"
		},
		{
			"id": "atomic-notes",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -280,
			"y": -360,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 130,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## 原子知识\n20-notes/\n\n一条笔记只承载一个可复用判断，并连接来源与领域"
		},
		{
			"id": "knowledge-types",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -280,
			"y": -150,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 150,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## 知识对象\nConcept / Claim / Method / Risk / Tool / Domain\n\n用 related、sources、domains 连接成网络"
		},
		{
			"id": "synthesis",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -280,
			"y": 80,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 140,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## 综合产物\n40-synthesis/\n\n领域地图、技术雷达、行业简报、实践手册、决策框架"
		},
		{
			"id": "cross-domain",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -280,
			"y": 270,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "## 跨领域连接\n同一概念可以被多个领域引用\n\n主归属保持唯一，跨领域关系用 related / secondary_domains 表达"
		},
		{
			"id": "group-storage",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 470,
			"y": -470,
			"width": 640,
			"height": 850,
			"color": "6",
			"label": "4. Storage, Index & Quality"
		},
		{
			"id": "markdown-store",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 540,
			"y": -370,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## Canonical Store\nGit + Markdown + Canvas\n\n先让文件系统成为长期事实源"
		},
		{
			"id": "catalog-index",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 540,
			"y": -190,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## 结构化索引\n70-indexes/catalog.json\n\n给 Codex 快速读 metadata、路径、标签、领域、置信度"
		},
		{
			"id": "semantic-index",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 540,
			"y": -10,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 140,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "## 后续增强\nSQLite FTS / Vector Index / Graph DB / MCP Memory\n\n等领域结构稳定后再接入"
		},
		{
			"id": "quality-monitor",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 540,
			"y": 190,
			"width": 500,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 质量与过期检查\nfreshness / confidence / evals / duplicate check\n\n变化快的事实必须刷新"
		},
		{
			"id": "group-codex",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 1290,
			"y": -470,
			"width": 620,
			"height": 850,
			"color": "2",
			"label": "5. Codex Consumption"
		},
		{
			"id": "retrieval",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1360,
			"y": -350,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## 检索\n按任务先筛领域，再检索 workflow / synthesis / notes / sources\n\n先窄后宽，避免上下文泛滥"
		},
		{
			"id": "context-pack",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1360,
			"y": -150,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 130,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## Context Pack\n50-workflows/\n\n把领域知识变成 Codex 可执行的项目上下文包"
		},
		{
			"id": "project-workflow",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1360,
			"y": 60,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 130,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## 项目工作流\n调研 / 架构 / 编码 / 评审 / 测试 / 上线\n\n在具体仓库中落地"
		},
		{
			"id": "feedback-loop",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1360,
			"y": 260,
			"width": 480,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "## 反馈回流\n项目经验、失败案例、复盘结论重新进入知识库"
		},
		{
			"id": "architecture-doc",
			"type": "file",
			"x": -1760,
			"y": 520,
			"width": 460,
			"height": 90,
