			"y": 520,
			"width": 540,
			"height": 90,
			"color": "3",
			"file": "30-maps/domains/domain-taxonomy-seed.md"
		},
		{
			"id": "source-quality-doc",
			"type": "file",
			"x": -1110,
			"y": 650,
			"width": 540,
			"height": 90,
			"color": "1",
			"file": "docs/source-quality.md"
		},
		{
			"id": "question-card",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -330,
			"y": 520,
			"width": 800,
			"height": 190,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "## 待继续补充的问题\n\n- 第一批顶层知识领域是否够用？哪些要拆分或合并？\n- 每个来源是否必须有 primary_domain？\n- 跨领域知识如何避免重复建档？\n- GitHub 技术主题、论文、个人经验分别需要哪些领域路由规则？"
		},
		{
			"id": "workflow-doc",
			"type": "file",
			"x": 1290,
			"y": 520,
			"width": 520,
			"height": 90,
			"color": "2",
			"file": "50-workflows/codex/kb-retrieval-context-pack.md"
		},
